In the wide, endless stretch of snow and ice, Chonky lives with a heart full of laughter and a body so round it only makes him more endearing. He waves at seagulls, plays with seals, and sprinkles happiness wherever he goes. Chonky reminds us of something simple: even in the coldest places, there’s always room for laughter, warmth, and true friendship.
